 - Add example poissonsystem.form
 - Modifications for new version of FIAT (FIAT-L)
   FIAT version 0.1 a factor 5 slower (no memoization)
   FIAT version 0.1.1 a little faster, only a factor 2 slower
 - Add setup.py script
